    <item>
      <title>刹车故障的宝马加剧了德国工业危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/bmw-cuts-guidance-after-faulty-components-prompt-recall</link>
      <description><![CDATA[宝马汽车公司警告称，由于大陆汽车制动系统存在故障，该公司将召回约 150 万辆汽车，这将导致其今年的利润下降，从而加剧欧洲最大经济体的工业危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/bmw-cuts-guidance-after-faulty-components-prompt-recall</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 10:56:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国人民银行中国债券交易量激增 显示出干预迹象</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/pboc-owned-china-bonds-see-trading-surge-in-sign-of-intervention</link>
      <description><![CDATA[交易员发现，一些主要由央行持有的中国特别国债的交易量激增，这一迹象表明，当局可能已更加积极地出售其持有的债券，以给火热的股市上涨降温。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/pboc-owned-china-bonds-see-trading-surge-in-sign-of-intervention</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 08:32:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>宝马下调业绩预期后，汽车股领跌欧洲股市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/rebound-in-european-stocks-fizzles-out-before-us-inflation-ecb</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股市下跌，汽车板块因宝马下调业绩预期领跌。美国通胀数据和欧洲央行会议公布前，投资者也持谨慎态度。]]></description>
